biography: Joakim is a golfer known for his meticulous approach to the game. While his home club remains a mystery, his presence is always noted on the course.
He has participated once in past Hector Trophée events. Though he is yet to secure a victory at the Hector Trophée or claim a Victor trophy, his dedication is clear.

Although Joakim is not currently slated to participate in the upcoming Hector Trophée 2025, fans know that he remains an active player in Hector events and that his return to future competitions is always a possibility.
